- `styles/main.css`: `.rebel-section` (warning/active variants, pulse animation), `.map-tt-owner--rebel`.

**T152 — Dynastic Succession System:**
- `src/systems/dynasty.js`: New file. `HEIR_DEFS` (warrior/diplomat/scholar). `initDynasty()` (idempotent). `dynastyTick()` fires `SUCCESSION_EVENT` at `nextSuccessionTick` (every 2400 ticks = 10 min), sets `pendingSuccession + successionDeadline` (+120 ticks). Auto-chooses random heir + applies regency (480 ticks, −20% rates) if deadline passes. Ends regency on tick expiry. `chooseHeir(type)` validates and applies heir, sets next succession tick. `getSuccessionSecsLeft()` + `getRegencySecsLeft()` for UI countdown.
