- `src/core/state.js`: Added `state.dynasty = null`; `initState()` resets to null.
- `src/systems/resources.js`: T152 block after T150 — diplomat heir +0.5 gold/s, scholar heir +0.5 mana/s, regency penalty ×0.80 all positive rates while `regencyUntil > tick`.
- `src/systems/research.js`: scholar heir multiplies research rate by 1.10 (stacks with Great Works).
- `src/systems/combat.js`: Warrior heir +15% attackPower in both `getAttackPreview` and `attackTile` (after T150 Grand Theory block).
- `index.html`: Succession modal with backdrop + 3 heir option buttons (⚔️/🤝/📚) + countdown `<span>`.
