## 2026-04-20 — Session N+31

**Tasks completed:** T123, T124

**Summary:**
All prior tasks (T001–T122) were complete. Created T123+T124 task specs then implemented two Phase 45 features: Notification Center (T123) adding a persistent event history drawer in the title bar, and Empire Legacy Traits (T124) adding cross-game meta-progression via localStorage-persisted legacy points and purchasable starting bonuses.

**T123 — Notification Center:**
