- `game/src/systems/combat.js` — attackTile(x,y) validates adjacency/fog/ownership, sums unit attack with tech multipliers (tactics ×1.25, steel ×1.5, engineering ×1.1), probabilistic outcome (win chance = power/(power+defense)), captures tile + grants loot on win, loses 1 unit on defeat
