**Architecture decisions:**
- Tile defense scales linearly with distance: `15 + dist * 6` (reachable with 3–5 units at start)
- Combat is probabilistic: `winChance = clamp(0.1, 0.9, power / (power + defense))`
- Territory bonuses are stateless — recalcRates() recomputes from scratch each time; no delta tracking needed
- Map stored in localStorage as part of save state (version 2); backwards compat: if no map in save, initMap() generates fresh one
- Military panel UI fully reactive via existing UNIT_CHANGED / BUILDING_CHANGED events

