**T090 — Building Specializations:**

**Files created/modified:**
- `game/src/data/buildingSpecials.js` (new): 8 SPECIALIZATION entries across 4 buildings. Farm: `granary` (+200 food cap, ×0.9 food) / `market_garden` (×1.3 food, +0.5 gold/s). LumberMill: `timber_mill` (×1.4 wood) / `charcoal_forge` (×0.8 wood, +0.5 iron/s, requires metalworking). Barracks: `training_grounds` (×0.75 train time) / `armory` (×1.15 combat, requires metalworking). Quarry: `deep_quarry` (×1.4 stone) / `iron_quarry` (×1.3 stone, +0.5 iron/s, requires metalworking). `SPECIALS_BY_BUILDING` and `ELIGIBLE_BUILDINGS` exports.
