- `game/src/systems/resources.js`: Imported SPECIALIZATIONS; building loop now reads `state.buildingSpecials[id]` to get specDef; applies `specDef.prodMult[res]` per resource on building production; after loop applies `specDef.rateBonus` (flat rates) and `specDef.capBonus` (cap bumps).
- `game/src/systems/combat.js`: Added Armory +15% multiplier in both `getAttackPreview()` and `attackTile()` after council boon mult.
- `game/src/ui/buildingPanel.js`: Imported `specializeBuilding + SPECIALIZATIONS + SPECIALS_BY_BUILDING + ELIGIBLE_BUILDINGS`; subscribed `BUILDING_SPECIALIZED → render`; added `_specializationsSection()` — only visible when player owns ≥1 eligible building; active-spec shows gold-bordered card with spec badge + desc; un-specialized shows 2 option cards with affordability-coded cost, desc, Specialize button (disabled when tech/gold requirements not met); click delegate handles `specialize` action.
