**T118 — Hero Enshrinement System:**

**Files created/modified:**
- `game/src/systems/heroSystem.js`: Added `import recalcRates`; `LEGACY_RATES_BY_SKILL` constant mapping each of 10 hero skills to a permanent resource rate bonus at ~50% power (e.g. `battle_hardened→{gold:0.4}`, `logistics→{food:0.3,wood:0.2}`, `arcane_attunement→{mana:0.25}`); exported `ENSHRINE_MAX=2`, `ENSHRINE_PRESTIGE=200`; `canEnshrineHero()` validates recruited + 3 skills + 10 combat wins + below max; `enshrineHero()` computes cumulative rates, appends legacy to `state.heroLegacy.enshrined`, clears `state.hero`, calls `recalcRates()`, emits `HERO_ENSHRINED+HERO_CHANGED+RESOURCE_CHANGED`, logs message.
