- `game/styles/main.css`: `.dipl-campaign` section, `.campaign-active` progress bar, `.btn--campaign` launch buttons, `.campaign-cooldown`, `.campaign-launch-row`.
- `game/src/main.js`: Imports, `registerSystem(campaignTick)`, `initCampaigns()` in boot+`_newGame`, save/load (version 45).

**Architecture decisions:**
- Celestial effects applied via `state.celestial.active.type` checks directly in each system (resources, research, combat, spells) — avoids circular imports since celestialEvents.js needs to call recalcRates() from resources.js.
- Campaign loot mult applied at the same point as hero lootMult and streakLoot in `_victory()`. Campaign wins only counted on non-barbarian, non-rebel tile captures matching the target empire.
- Save version bumped to 45 for both T153+T154. Both systems use `?? null` defaults in _applySave for backwards compatibility.

