- `game/src/systems/weather.js`: `_spawnWeather()` initialises `state.weatherMemory` if null, increments `counts[chosen.id]`, and at count ≥ 3 sets `adaptations[chosen.id]=true`, emits `WEATHER_ADAPTED`, logs windfall toast. Threshold constant `WEATHER_ADAPT_THRESHOLD = 3`.
