**Architecture decisions:**
- No save version bump: both new state fields use `?? null` defaults in `_applySave()` so older saves load cleanly.
- Weather adaptation halving uses `1-(1-mult)*0.5` to cut the penalty in half rather than eliminating it entirely, preserving game challenge while rewarding persistence.
- Surge Provisions expiry is tracked purely via tick comparison (`surgeExpiresAt > state.tick`) — no new tick system needed; the military panel TICK handler already re-renders every 16 ticks when `hasSurgeActivity` is true.

