**T160 — Lifetime Empire Records:**

**Files modified:**
- `game/src/data/lifetimeRecords.js` (new file): `RECORD_DEFS` array (8 records: longestGame, mostGoldEarned, mostPopulation, mostBuildings, mostTechResearched, mostTerritory, mostTradeRoutes, mostPrestige). `getRecords()` reads from `'empireos-records'` localStorage key. `updateRecords()` snapshots current game state, updates any beaten highs, and persists.
- `game/src/main.js`: Imports `updateRecords`. `on(Events.GAME_OVER, () => updateRecords())` listener added. `updateRecords()` also called at the top of `_newGame()` before state wipe.
- `game/src/ui/settingsPanel.js`: Imports `getRecords`, `RECORD_DEFS`. `on(Events.GAME_OVER, ...)` re-render listener added. `_recordsSection()` renders a `settings-section` with a grid of 8 record rows (icon + label + personal best value). Injected in `_render()` after `_weatherAdaptationsSection()`.
